<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.9">
<l>vaṅkamali taṭaṅkaṭaluḷ vāṉavarka ḷōṭu māmuṉivar palarkūṭi māmalarkaḷ tūvi</l>
<l>eṅkaḷtaṉi nāyakaṉē yemakkaruḷā yeṉṉu mīcaṉavaṉ makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>ceṅkayalum vāḷaikaḷuñ cenneliṭaik kutippac cēlukaḷuñ ceḻumpaṇaicūḻ vītitoṟum miṭaintu</l>
<l>maṅkulmati yakaṭuriñcu maṇimāṭa nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">with jeweled mansions, on which the moon in the sky rubs its belly,</l>
<l>Crowding in every street surrounded by fertile ponds where carp frolic,</l>
<l rend="indent">as rosy kayal and vāḷai [fish] leap in the midst of red paddy fields,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the god, happily with affection [and] rejoicing,</l>
<l rend="indent">to whom many great sages</l>
<l>Joining with celestials in the wide sea [of milk] where waves swell,</l>
<l rend="indent">scattering large blossoms, call “Our sole master! Be gracious to us!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
